Thika Power of Kenya Plans to Build 87-Megawatt Plant, the Nation Reports

-- B y   P a u l   R i c h a r d s o n
-- 
2011-07-23T08:10:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-23/thika-power-of-kenya-plans-to-build-87-megawatt-plant-the-nation-reports.html
Thika Power Ltd. plans to build an
87-megawatt power plant, according to a statement published by
the company in the Saturday Nation newspaper today.  The plant will be built at Thika, 40 kilometers (25 miles)
north of the capital, Nairobi, after the company has acquired a
license from the Energy Regulatory Commission, it said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  